  "title": "Junior Brand & Events Crew!",
  "description": "<p>A fun, hands-on role for those who love people, teamwork, and lively environments!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join our Junior Brand &amp; Events Crew, where you’ll help bring events and brand experiences to life. If you want a role that helps you grow confidence and communication skills — this is for you.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You’ll Be Doing:</p>\n<p>🎤 Engaging with business owners</p>\n<p>🎯 Driving and supporting on-ground operations</p>\n<p>🚀 Representing brands with professionalism and energy</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Who We’re Looking For:</p>\n<p>✨ Outgoing personalities</p>\n<p>✨ No experience needed — training provided</p>\n<p>✨ Team players who enjoy fast-paced environments</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you want a job that’s dynamic and never boring —</p>\n<p>📩 Apply to join our Events Crew!</p>",
